  <title translate="true">RMA: Stress Periods</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">RMA: Stress Periods</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This model is a steady state model. &#160;The length of the single stress period is 20 years which corresponds to 631152000 seconds (20 years*365.25 days/year *24 hr/day*3600 sec/hr).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure Referrer"><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true">Select </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Model|MODFLOW Time...</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> to display the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MODFLOW_Time_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">MODFLOW Time</link><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> dialog box (fig. 108). &#160;Enter 0 for the time of the </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Starting time</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> of the first stress period and 631152000 for the </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Ending time</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true">. Set the </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Max first time step length</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> to 631152000 as well so that </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Number of steps</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> in the stress period is 1. Make sure the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Drawdown reference</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> check box is unchecked. Click </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> to close the dialog box.</text></para>
